# Code Refactor (React / Vue)

When asked to refactor, migrate, or transform code, follow:
`.claude/skills/refactor/SKILL.md`

## Quick Reference

**Usage:** `/refactor [react|vue] <transform> [--scope <glob>] [--dry-run]`

**Transforms:** class-to-hooks, options-to-composition, cjs-to-esm, tanstack-v4-to-v5, custom

**BANNED:** Transforming test files, changing public API without BREAKING flag

For full protocol: read `.claude/skills/refactor/SKILL.md`
